title: Press'd Juice Bar and Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Juice bar and scratch kitchen. Serves cold pressed as well custom juices, smoothies with option of house-made almond mylk, a daily soup, and a small menu of wraps and snacks. Originally est. 2013 as The Juice Bar of Winter Garden at 100 W Plant St Ste 140 and rebranded in 2015 and moved into Plant Street Market.
